name: Tiskihaamu
description:
Why should we be afraid of ghosts? Look how helpful they can be...


In my previous apartement in Helsinki, the kitchen had a special door that led to the hallway. It was used in the early 1900s by the housekeepers to access directly the kitchen without bothering the gentlefolk. 

Dedicated to everyone who hates doing the dishes.

Cardboard print, 12x10
